All the chiefs who follow Great Chief Moong are dangerous. None should still be alive. It's terrible, but it's the only way.

If you take this tablet to the humans, they'll probably be able to help.

Huh. Conquer all non-tuwangis? That's absolute jibberish, besides the fact that we're quickly running out of tree-growing land, what with the swamp expanding like it is.

Thanks for bringing this to me. We've clearly got some work to do if we're going to stop it before it gets out of control.
